---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Complete Guide to Personal Training Marketing in Canada | Lead Flow North">
  <article class="py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <!-- Back Link -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-8">
        <a href="/industries/fitness-gyms/personal-training" class="inline-flex items-center text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-700 font-medium">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path></svg>
          Back to Personal Training
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <header class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <span class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Personal Training</span>
          <span class="text-slate-500 text-sm">12 min read</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">
          The Complete Guide to Personal Training Marketing Automation
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-8">
          Build consistent income with systems that convert consultations, retain clients, and generate referrals automatically.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate max-w-none">
          
          <p class="lead text-xl text-slate-700 mb-8">
            Personal trainers excel at training but often struggle with the business side. Inconsistent income and client churn make it hard to build a sustainable practice. Automation changes everything.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">Consultation Conversion</h2>

          <p>
            Free consultations mean nothing if people don't show. Automated confirmations, reminders, and prep emails dramatically increase show rates and set the stage for conversion.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">Between-Session Accountability</h2>

          <p>
            Clients don't just need trainingâ€”they need accountability. Automated check-ins between sessions keep clients engaged, on track, and less likely to skip.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">Referral Generation</h2>

          <p>
            Your best clients are your best marketing. Automated referral requests timed after milestone achievements turn happy clients into lead-generating machines.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-600 p-8 rounded-xl text-white my-12">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Ready to Build Your Business?</h3>
            <p class="text-blue-100 mb-6">
              Get a free consultation and see exactly how we'd implement these automations for your personal training business.
            </p>
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center bg-white text-blue-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-slate-100 transition">
              Book Your Free Demo
            </a>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
